room_title: Escape room "Escape the Roxbury" by Green Light Escape Room in Wilmington
room_address: 130 N. Front St. Suite 202 Wilmington, NC 28401a
room_description: You and your team are the worst FBI agents the Bureau has ever seen and you’ve been tasked with stopping the most notoriously incompetent criminal “mastermind” in modern history. You must go undercover at Wilmington’s hottest club and stop him. Brace yourselves for epic one-liners and laugh yourself to the end of the mission.
